<br />
<br />function foo(){
<br />  var a = 1;
<br />  fffffffffffffffff
<br />  var b = 2;
<br />}
<br />
<br />The bug, "fffffffffffffffff" will raise an exception, cause the debugger to run, and allow you to choose which debugger to use.  Do not use numbers or function names.
